<p>Stepping out: The Bachelor's Roxi Kenny was pictured out and about in Brisbane on Friday following her exit from the show</p>

<p>She was dressed casually in a black dress, a matching bag, and a pair of Givenchy slides.</p>

<p>Roxi dramatically stormed out of the mansion on Thursday's episode, after her feud with Juliette.</p>

<p>And the 29-year-old has revealed the real reason she tearfully left the series while speaking to The Courier Mail on Friday.</p>

